Female imago
(in alcohol, reared from larva) (

). Length (mm): body 4.7; fore wings, 5.0; caudal filaments, 4.5. Head, thorax and abdomen yellowish brown; thorax somewhat darker than abdomen. Wings hyaline, all veins pale. Legs pale. Abdomen with eggs yellowish or brownish; abdominal sterna yellowish. Subanal plate triangular with rounded apex. Caudal filaments pale.

